        <h2>Food</h2>
        <p>
            Food is any substance consumed to provide nutritional support for an organism, offering energy, growth, and life
            maintenance. It is typically of plant, animal, or fungal origin and contains essential nutrients like
            carbohydrates,
            fats, proteins, vitamins, and minerals. Eating a variety of healthy foods is crucial for staying alive, staying
            active,
            and preventing disease.
        </p>
